===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}}, from {{etyl|xno|en}} {{term|muntaine|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|VL.|en}} {{m|la|*montānea}}, feminine of {{m|la|*montāneus||mountainous}}, alteration of {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|montānus}}, from {{term|mōns|||mountain|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*monti}} (compare Welsh {{term|mynydd||mountain|lang=cy}}, Albanian {{term|mat||bank, shore|lang=sq}}, Avestan {{rfscript|ae}} {{term||tr=mati||promontory|lang=ae}}), from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{m|ine-pro|*men-||to project, stick out}}. More at [[menace]].

